# Trading Tools (Work In Progress)

## Realtime Crypto Trading View

1. Fetch data in realtime using data.py
- Fetch OHLC data from Binance Futures and update it in realtime.
- Save all data to data/data.csv

2. Compute strategy & indicators using strategy.py
- Listen for changes in data/data.csv file.
- Apply strategy to given data each time the data file is updated
- Generate strategy.csv file containing result

3. Plot price & indicators using dashboard.py
- Plot chart and indicators 


--- How to use --
Run data.py, strategy.py and dashboard.py simultaneously.
Click on the given link from dashboard.py to access the chart.